          %h6 Getting underway with your product idea is exciting. Coshx helps get startups get on the road with ideation, design and product planning that set a course toward success.
        %li
          =image_tag 'front-page-mvp.png'
          %h5 Beyond MVP
          %h6 You’ve tested out the prototype. When it’s time to ramp up to full-featured app Coshx will get you there.
        %li
          =image_tag 'tech_craft.png'
          %h5 Scaling Up
          %h6 Lean on our experience to as you build out your product road map helping you make smart investments in your technology future.
